{
  "name": "Not Allowed To Die",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/life/heart-area-circle-red-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You believe that medical shinobi deaths should be the absolute last thing to happen on the battlefield. </p><p>Beyond all other circumstances, you are not allowed to die before your team does. </p><p>So long as another allied creature is initiative and they have 1 or more hit points, once per rest, you ignore effects of jutsu, features or traits from hostile creatures that would automatically kill you or reduce you to 0 hit points, instead being reduced to 1 hit point.</p>",
